tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Elliot.-Credit-Chris-Floyd-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Elliot.-Credit-Chris-Floyd-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Elliot.-Credit-Chris-Floyd-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Elliot.-Credit-Chris-Floyd-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Rialto">Rialto</a>宣布了他们的新专辑《Neon &amp; Ghost Signs》，并分享了伦敦演出的细节和亲密内容。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/steve-lamacqs-ten-forgotten-90s-indie-bands-need-know-2462733">Steve Lamacq 精选了 10 首伟大但被遗忘的 90 年代英国独立歌曲 - 您知道多少首？</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《Neon &amp; Ghost Signs》由 Tam Johnstone 和 Rialto 主唱 Louis Eliot 制作，Cenzo Townsend 混音，将于 4 月 25 日通过 Fierce Panda Records 发行，这将是该乐队 24 年来的首张唱片。</p><p> “Neon &amp; Ghost Signs” 可供预订，包括限量版独立商店独家透明绿色夜光乙烯基、白色乙烯基和限量版透明霓虹粉红色乙烯基以及CD 和盒式磁带。您可以<a href="https://eu-west-1.protection.sophos.com/?d=linktr.ee&amp;u=aHR0cHM6Ly9saW5rdHIuZWUvcmlhbHRvX25lb25hbmRnaG9zdHNpZ25z&amp;p=m&amp;i=NWVlYTAzZjk3NjFmMzEwZGUxYzNhMjM0&amp;t=b0JlSEZjUTdHQzNDZFdXRWttS1IydWticDRqYnRXVzJPc0pYMGJPTmhaQT0=&amp;h=6663e967a9444b6284179b9622736bdb&amp;s=AVNPUEhUT0NFTkNSWVBUSVbNdReq1m8-JGNlCxPjeBd-idEfINcqckkLDfSI1KKO0g" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订并预先保存专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3828454" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828454" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828454" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Rialto - &#39;Neon &amp; Ghost Signs&#39; 专辑插图。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rialto-Neon-Ghost-Signs-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828454" class="wp-caption-text"> Rialto – &#39;Neon &amp; Ghost Signs&#39; 专辑艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“霓虹灯与幽灵标志”的曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“没人让这个迪斯科舞厅活着”</strong><br /> <strong>2.《我想要你》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“霓虹灯和幽灵标志”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“让我不再紧张”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“记住忘记”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“永远不会来的车”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“砂纸之吻”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“樱桃”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“让你暂停”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“走了”</strong></p><p>这张专辑的第一个试听者以主打单曲“No One Leaves This Discotheque Alive”的形式出现，这是一首时髦的、合成器重的歌曲，让人想起 80 年代的俱乐部音乐。据一份新闻稿称，艾略特在这首歌曲中将自己塑造成“伦敦镇的猎犬，床单上沾满了金色”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="没有人让这个迪斯科舞厅活着（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6KejdccSxBU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Rialto 还宣布将于 5 月 14 日在伦敦 Scala 举行一场亲密演出。门票将于 1 月 15 日开始预售，粉丝们可以在<a href="https://eu-west-1.protection.sophos.com/?d=rialtomusic.com&amp;u=aHR0cHM6Ly9yaWFsdG9tdXNpYy5jb20v&amp;p=m&amp;i=NWVlYTAzZjk3NjFmMzEwZGUxYzNhMjM2&amp;t=aS9BY3BWN0VYRi9IQm5VMUlvdEJmK2MvbG0rU3VNZE1uVHFFMG5qNjVPZz0=&amp;h=6c497f